        <section class="section-features js--section-features" id="aboutus">
            <div class="row">
                <h2>Get food fast &mdash; not fast food.</h2>
                <p class="long-copy">
                    Hello, we’re HideOut, your new premium ethnic food service. We know you’re always busy. No time for cooking. So let us take care of that, we’re really good at it, we promise!
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
